responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "41F8587148A1400BBE68E98EA79792B0", "It is close. I can sense it. That is what brought me here to the Riverlands. Now I shall be consumed by a new reaping, a new Blood Blight It is my fate for defiling the Prime Harvester. Repent before you pass. REPENT!")
